default1. default              defaultWhat, if any, targets do youdefault set for your police force? What impact do you think this has on police recording crime practices?default&#xa0;
default1.1
default              
defaultI share the commonly held concern that setting targets can encourage "massaging" of statistics, and I welcome the current Government’s drive to remove t
defaulthem. 
default&#xa0;
default1.2
default              
defaultHowever, from a localism point of view, the public of 
defaultDorset
default made it clear to me that some areas of policing were in need of improvement, and therefore I have set some targets; although few compared to most other Forces.
