default1.10
default              
defaultIn relation to the second part of the question, some targets are very difficult to manipulate, for example the target set in relation to how long 
defaultstaff take to answer a non-emergency
default call. This is derived electronically from a database. 
default&#xa0;
default1.11
default              
defaultHowever, I am the first to appreciate that one of my targets, the positive outcome rate, could drive manipulation and perverse behaviour. 
default&#xa0;
default1.12
default              
defaultI considered 
defaultthis when setting the target, and I will answer below in Question 2 what we do to ensure this does not happen.
default&#xa0;
default1.13
default              
defaultI did not set targets without good reason. For example, the main targets above are addressing the two key issues the public told me they ha
defaultd with Dorset Police, namely:
default&#xa0;
default&#xa0;
default1.14
default              
defaultIn relation, statistically, to the number of criminals caught, 
defaultthe detection rate had to be addressed. 
default 
defaultDorset
default was one of the worst perfor
defaultming 
defaultf
defaultorces in the country when I was elected. The media reported on this with worrying headlines such as "
defaultOnly 
default1 in 5 criminals in 
defaultDorset
default caught". I had to 
defaultdeal with this
default.  
default&#xa0;
default1.15
default              
defaultSo, any 
defaulttarget set was 
defaultput there f
defaultor a good reason. 
defaultAnd such targets allow me to hold the Chief Constable to account over that particular area. 
default&#xa0;
default1.16
default              
defaultFor example, although the detection rate has risen steadily since my election, the performance in the call handling system, 101, declined month on month last
default year, and the targets set allowed me to see this, and formally challenge accordingly.
default&#xa0;
default1.17
default              
defaultThis challenge has worked - performance in the Police Enquiry Centre has improved dramatically since July. 
